<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; }
  .container { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
  h2 { color: #c0392b; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .subtitle { color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0; }
  th { background: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left; font-size: 14px; }
  td { padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 14px; }
  tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafafa; }
  .level-주의 { color: #e67e22; font-weight: bold; }
  .level-경고 { color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; }
  .level-위험 { color: #8e44ad; font-weight: bold; }
  .level-급락 { color: #c0392b; font-weight: bold; }
  .level-급등 { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; }
  .cta { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 12px 28px; background: #2980b9; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 15px; }
  .footer { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 12px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <h2>📊 주식 지표 임계치 알림</h2>
  <div class="subtitle">{{ triggered|length }}개 지표가 설정된 임계치에 도달했습니다.</div>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>지표</th>
        <th>단계</th>
        <th>현재 값</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for item in triggered %}
      <tr>
        <td>{{ item.indicator }}</td>
        <td><span class="level-{{ item.level }}">{{ item.level }}</span></td>
        <td>{{ "%.4f"|format(item.value) }}</td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <a href="{{ site_url }}" class="cta">대시보드 바로가기 →</a>

  <div class="footer">
    본 메일은 자동 발송입니다. 투자 조언이 아닌 정보 제공 목적입니다.<br>
    대시보드: <a href="{{ site_url }}">{{ site_url }}</a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
